<div class="mission">
  <div class="mission-content">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <hr />
    <p>Case Law strives to be <span>your guide</span> throughout your legal matters. Most people are thrust involuntarily into a legal issue, but not everyone needs a lawyer. We provide <span>free resources</span> to help you understand your situation and make informed decisions (with no obligation to work with us!). If you decide you need a lawyer, we agree with you that it is a personal decision not to be taken lightly. We aren't the best fit for everyone, but we are happy to help connect you with the best lawyers we know. If we end up working together, we will provide an <span>excellent and transparent experience</span> for you. We value your trust and regard for us, and we will always do our best to help. Thank you for the opportunity to serve you, and we wish the very best for you and your loved ones!</p>
  </div>
</div>
