          Other areas
        </div>
        <div class="card-copy">
          <p>Do you need a will? Are you fighting a traffic ticket? Have you been charged with a felony/misdemeanor? Even if we aren't the best fit for you and your case, we will do our best to help you find the lawyer who is.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
